{"tid":2424141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生受查期間自稱曾與同學晚膳 警方指疑與事實不符 控以誤導警務人員罪","createTime":"2021-02-26T10:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T13:58:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0b18d32bef25531b28fe1be1ea8139c62c0e0ed5","tid":2424141,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:41:11.000Z","msg":"警方去年在旺角警署調查16歲男生涉於去年8月31日非法集結的案件，男生指自己案發時與同學晚飯，惟警方向其同學調查後，發現男生疑說謊。男生未被落案起訴非法集結，卻先遭控以一項誤導警務人員罪，今日在西九龍裁判法庭提堂。案件押後至4月13日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告為16歲盧姓男學生，被控一項誤導警務人員罪，控罪指他於去年9月28日在旺角警署接見室3號明知地提供虛假資料，企圖誤導偵緝警10354，亦即聲稱他於去年8月31日晚上與一名廖姓同學在旺角區晚餐；但事實上被告並沒有在上述日期與上述的廖姓人士晚餐。<br />\n<br />\n控方指已準備好答辯，但辯方申請押後案件，以待索取文件及給予法律意見。控方不反對被告保釋，惟要求施加額外的保釋條件。主任裁判官羅德泉批准被告以2,000元現金保釋，同時須居於報稱地址、每晚10時至翌早7時宵禁，以及不可接觸控方證人。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被告曾遭警方以非法集結罪名拘捕。警方及後向廖姓朋友調查，發現沒有被告所稱的事，其後再次拘捕被告。至於男生所涉的非法集結罪則暫未落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/XKD6BIJSUVAUVIDSG4OKGKRTIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FXKD6BIJSUVAUVIDSG4OKGKRTIA%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=34ab52cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FXKD6BIJSUVAUVIDSG4OKGKRTIA%2F&h=ccb8e584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/XKD6BIJSUVAUVIDSG4OKGKRTIA/</a>"},{"pid":"bc140a9053b9f1a3234ebc79acf1ac064fcc48a4","tid":2424141,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a8c336f203cd0450e506e71b24ee4e62182dcf","tid":2424141,"uid":4493,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"主任裁判官羅德泉批准被告以2,000元現金保釋<br />\n<br />\n好似係佢幾個月來第一次俾人保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91c492122a3986469cf9ccb3cdf8a5f1093caac","tid":2424141,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"據了解，被告因涉及 8 月 31 日的非法集結被調查，其間疑謊稱當晚相約同學用膳，<span class=\"red\">惟警方向該名同學查問後，發現有人疑似提供不實資料</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-31-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%9B%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%86%B3-16-%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%BD%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-31-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%259B%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%2586%25B3-16-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%258E%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=b4709e81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F8-31-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%259B%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%2586%25B3-16-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%258E%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&h=bcf2b981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/8-31-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%9B%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%86%B3-16-%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%BD%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"6c0bb925ed6f26741fcec99bbcde0bb08b929763","tid":2424141,"uid":172172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27a8c336f203cd0450e506e71b24